<HL>
   Enterprise:
   Bio-Control Sector Learns Lessons on Client Education
   ---
   Growers of Pest-Fighting Insects Are
   Bugged by Confusion on Many Fronts
   ----
   By Mark Robichaux
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
08/29/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B2
</SO>
<MS>
BASIC MATERIALS (BSC)
</MS>
