<LEADPARA>  YOU know how it is: You're sitting down for your morning cup of coffee when
you spot a dark spot out of the corner of your eye. Pow! Your morning paper is
instantly transformed into a fly swatter and another insect joins the dead bug
hall of fame.;    But oh no! There's another bug! And another, and pretty soon
you've gone, well, buggy.  </LEADPARA>
